= ruby-usb - libusb binding for Ruby
<%
  def project
    "ruby-usb"
  end

  def version
    File.read("VERSION").chomp
  end
%>

ruby-usb is a libusb binding library for Ruby.

== Author

Tanaka Akira <akr@fsij.org>

== Home Page

((<URL:http://www.a-k-r.org/ruby-usb/>))

== License

LGPL

== Feature

* direct (non-rubyish) binding
* rubyish interface (work in progress)

== Download

* latest release: ((<<%=project%>-<%=version%>.tar.gz|URL:<%=project%>-<%=version%>.tar.gz>))

* development version in Subversion repository:

    % svn co svn://svn@svn.a-k-r.org/akr/<%=project%>/trunk <%=project%>

== Install

  % ruby extconf.rb 
  % make
  % make install

